<section class="stage-page teaser-screen">
  <header class="question-header teaser-screen__header">
    <a class="back-button question-header__back question-actions__back" href="/" aria-label="Volver">
      <span aria-hidden="true">‹</span>
    </a>
    <p class="eyebrow">Tus instintos primarios</p>
  </header>

  <article class="question-card-panel teaser-card">
    <div class="question-card-panel__body teaser-card__body">
      <div class="teaser-card__copy">
        <h2 class="teaser-card__headline mb-0">Una primera aproximaci&oacute;n a tu mapa interno</h2>
        <p class="teaser-card__summary mb-0">
          Este test b&aacute;sico recoge se&ntilde;ales iniciales sobre tus impulsos, estilo de respuesta y energ&iacute;a
          predominante. No busca etiquetarte de forma definitiva, sino abrir una lectura inicial con
          sentido.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="question-card-panel__selection teaser-card__insight">
      <span class="question-card-panel__selection-label">Qu&eacute; esperar</span>
      <strong class="question-card-panel__selection-value">
        Responder&aacute;s <%= pageData.hookCount %> afirmaciones breves y luego ver&aacute;s una lectura inicial antes de profundizar.
      </strong>
    </div>
  </article>

  <form action="/quick-test/start" method="post" class="question-actions teaser-screen__actions">
    <button class="btn btn-primary app-cta question-actions__next" type="submit">
      Empezar
    </button>
  </form>
</section>
